o meet you too...&quot; She slowly uncovered the blankflank, seeing she caught the hint easily.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404985378";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#760090";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14049853824";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#872995";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:795859;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"795859";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10598";s:6:"handle";s:15:"Radiant_Revelry";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"645";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Mystery";s:4:"text";s:260:"/me began to move some and spoke out with a small &#039;try to cheer you up&#039; tone of voice. &quot;You know your not the only adult without a cutie mark, In fact I know one right here in ponyville. You don&#039;t have anything to be shy about at all!&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404985544";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#aab589";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14049855434";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#13d3bd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:795872;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"795872";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10623";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Mystery";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"752";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:15:"Radiant_Revelry";s:4:"text";s:162:"/me nods, and finally uncovers the blankflank fully, &quot;Even then, it still feels weird to once in a while have somepony look,&quot; She gives an amused smirk.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404985688";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#760090";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14049856919";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#872995";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:795874;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"795874";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10598";s:6:"handle";s:15:"Radiant_Revelry";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"645";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Mystery";s:4:"text";s:165:"/me catches the smirk and smirks back &quot;I like to guess a pony&#039;s name using her cutie mark. It&#039;s pretty fun, you should try it some time mystery.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404985767";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#aab589";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14049857669";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#13d3bd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:795883;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"795883";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10623";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Mystery";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"752";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:15:"Radiant_Revelry";s:4:"text";s:97:"/me nods, and glances to the mare&#039;s cutiemark. She smirks to it, &quot;Nice cutiemark.&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404986053";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#760090";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14049860572";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#872995";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:795887;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"795887";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10598";s:6:"handle";s:15:"Radiant_Revelry";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"645";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:7:"Mystery";s:4:"text";s:243:"&quot;Thanks, it&#039;s more of a social cutie mark if anything to be honest mystery. I have a tendency to get along with ponies really well! Funny enough though until it got my cutie mark I tended to avoid every pony, how silly is that?&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404986291";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#aab589";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14049862904";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#13d3bd";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:795890;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:6:"795890";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:5:"10623";s:6:"handle";s:7:"Mystery";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"752";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:15:"Radiant_Revelry";s:4:"text";s:229:"/me shrugs, &quot;I&#039;m still sort of that way...but I guess it is.&quot; She blushes lightly, &quot;So...do you live here in Ponyville, or are you visiting? I&#039;ve been here...I haven&#039;t seen you before though...&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1404986549";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#760090";s:9:"ch